---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Approach | EEDEE Law"
  description="At EEDEE Law, we believe in creativity within compliance, exploring every option before you choose, and making the law work for research, not against it."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <Hero 
      title="Our Approach"
      subtitle="We believe in creativity within compliance, in exploring every option before you choose, and in making the law work for research, not against it."
    />
    
    <!-- Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="section-spacing bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
              Law that works for research, not against it
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Most legal counsel tells you what you can't do. We tell you what you can.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none fade-in stagger-1">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              We believe clinical research should move faster without cutting corners, that innovation deserves encouragement rather than being buried under legal barriers, and that every organization, regardless of size, deserves counsel that understands their operational reality.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              We don't just know the regulations; we know the workflows. We don't just see the risks; we see the solutions.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              At EEDEE Law, we believe in creativity within compliance, in exploring every option before you choose, and in making the law work for research, not against it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Core Principles -->
    <section class="section-spacing bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Our Core Principles
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Four pillars that guide everything we do
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Goals-driven -->
          <div class="approach-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm fade-in stagger-1">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <img 
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768296684/auto-site-builder/Edye%20Edens%20Life%20Sciences%20Law%20Group/image_6.png" 
                  alt="Goals" 
                  class="w-12 h-12"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Goals-driven</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Lead with possibility instead of barriers</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  We start every conversation by understanding what you're trying to achieve. Then we work backward from your goals to find compliant pathways forward, not reasons why something can't be done.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Research-first -->
          <div class="approach-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm fade-in stagger-2">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <img 
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768296683/auto-site-builder/Edye%20Edens%20Life%20Sciences%20Law%20Group/image_7.png" 
                  alt="Research" 
                  class="w-12 h-12"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Research-first</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Operational reality over regulatory theory</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  We've lived in your world. We understand the difference between what regulations say and how research actually gets done. Our advice is grounded in operational reality, not theoretical compliance.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Constraints-empowered -->
          <div class="approach-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm fade-in stagger-3">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <img 
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768296684/auto-site-builder/Edye%20Edens%20Life%20Sciences%20Law%20Group/image_8.png" 
                  alt="Compliance" 
                  class="w-12 h-12"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Constraints-empowered</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We acknowledge constraints instead of demanding perfection</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Real organizations have real limitations—budget, staff, time, technology. We work within your constraints to build systems that are sustainable and actually implementable.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Decision-focused -->
          <div class="approach-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm fade-in stagger-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <img 
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768296684/auto-site-builder/Edye%20Edens%20Life%20Sciences%20Law%20Group/image_9.png" 
                  alt="Decision" 
                  class="w-12 h-12"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Decision-focused</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We provide you with all the options before you decide</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  We don't make decisions for you—we give you the information you need to make informed choices. Every option comes with clear risk assessments and practical implementation guidance.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Experience Section -->
    <section class="section-spacing bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="fade-in">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
              30+ Years of Clinical Research Experience
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
              We've spent over a decade in academic research administration. We speak your language.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Our experience spans HRPP operations, IRB management, research misconduct investigations, technology integration, and crisis management. We understand the pressures you face because we've faced them ourselves.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              This isn't theoretical knowledge—it's hard-earned experience from the trenches of clinical research operations.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="fade-in stagger-1">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What This Means for You</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 mr-3">•</span>
                  We understand your operational constraints
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 mr-3">•</span>
                  We know the difference between theory and practice
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 mr-3">•</span>
                  We speak the language of research administration
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 mr-3">•</span>
                  We've navigated the same challenges you face
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 mr-3">•</span>
                  We provide solutions that actually work
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section-spacing bg-gray-900 text-white">
      <div class="container-custom text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
            Ready to experience the difference?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Let's discuss how our approach can help your organization move faster with confidence.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary bg-white text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100">
            Start a Conversation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>